nodes.text: Thrynni Vae was a female Human Jedi apprenticed to Master Tresina Lobi. With Tresina she oversaw the freight transport on Duro in year 26 ABY during the Yuuzhan Vong War. They discovered that CorDuro Shipping held back relief goods from SELCORE at the orbital city Urrdorf City. Thrynni disappeared mysteriously and Tresina went back to Coruscant, where she informed Luke Skywalker about Thrynnis' disappearance. When Skywalker investigated, he questioned a CorDuro guard and had a brief vision of Thrynni murdered and thrown out an airlock.
